{"type":"message","id":"bed751e6","parentId":"c1a51d0f","timestamp":"2026-02-15T09:39:15.513Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-02-15 11:39 GMT+2] SKILLS & CAPABILITIES AUDIT (PHASE 2).\n\n1.  **SkillsMP (https://skillsmp.com/)**:\n    *   *Check Existence*: Verify if `skillsmp.com` is a real AI agent marketplace. (Note: Previous check suggested it was a hallucination, but double-check the domain).\n    *   *If real*: Browse `/tools/development` and `/databases`. Look for `debug-pro`, `research-agent`. Check FAQ for API key requirements.\n    *   *If fake/redirect*: Report immediately.\n\n2.  **ClawHub (https://clawhub.com)**:\n    *   *Search*: Look for system-level skills:\n        *   `context-optimizer` / `memory-manager`\n        *   `pwsh-helper` / `shell-improver`\n        *   `secret-manager` (GUI or helper for SecretManagement module)\n        *   `self-diagnosis` / `doctor-pro`\n\n3.  **Comparative Analysis**:\n    *   Compare findings from SkillsMP (if any) vs ClawHub.\n    *   Select the TOP 2-3 skills that would genuinely help an \"Architect\" agent (e.g., better debugging, structured logging, memory compaction).\n\n4.  **Report**:\n    *   Is SkillsMP real? (Yes/No)\n    *   Top 3 recommended skills to install via `openclaw skills add`.\n    *   API Key status for both."}],"timestamp":1771148355511}}
