          - heading \"Answer Overflow\" [level=3] [ref=e100]\n          - paragraph [ref=e101]: Search indexed Discord community discussions via Answer Overflow. Find solutions to coding problems, library issues, and community Q&A that only exist in Discord conversations.\n          - generic [ref=e103]:\n            - generic [ref=e104]:\n              - generic [ref=e105]: by\n              - generic [ref=e107]: \"@RhysSullivan\"\n            - generic [ref=e108]: ⭐ 24 · ⤓ 2613 · ⤒ 18\n    - generic [ref=e109]:\n      - heading \"Popular skills\" [level=2] [ref=e110]\n      - paragraph [ref=e111]: Most-downloaded, non-suspicious picks.\n      - generic [ref=e112]:\n        - link \"Gog Google Workspace CLI for Gmail, Calendar, Drive, Contacts, Sheets, and Docs. by @steipete ⭐ 78 · ⤓ 22784 · ⤒ 333\" [ref=e113] [cursor=pointer]:\n          - /url: /kn70pywhg0fyz996kpa8xj89s57yhv26/gog\n          - heading \"Gog\" [level=3] [ref=e114]\n          - paragraph [ref=e115]: Google Workspace CLI for Gmail, Calendar, Drive, Contacts, Sheets, and Docs.\n          - generic [ref=e117]:\n            - generic [ref=e118]:\n              - generic [ref=e119]: by\n              - generic [ref=e121]: \"@steipete\"\n            - generic [ref=e122]: ⭐ 78 · ⤓ 22784 · ⤒ 333\n        - link \"Wacli Send WhatsApp messages to other people or search/sync WhatsApp history via the wacli CLI (not for normal user chats). by @steipete ⭐ 43 · ⤓ 19856 · ⤒ 184\" [ref=e123] [cursor=pointer]:\n          - /url: /kn70pywhg0fyz996kpa8xj89s57yhv26/wacli\n          - heading \"Wacli\" [level=3] [ref=e124]\n          - paragraph [ref=e125]: Send WhatsApp messages to other people or search/sync WhatsApp history via the wacli CLI (not for normal user chats).\n          - generic [ref=e127]:\n            - generic [ref=e128]:\n              - generic [ref=e129]: by\n              - generic [ref=e131]: \"@steipete\"\n            - generic [ref=e132]: ⭐ 43 · ⤓ 19856 · ⤒ 184\n        - link \"Tavily Web Sear